data.description: Country living on 5 wooded acres!  This home has 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths with a 2 car attached garage.  The walk out lower level has 2 more rooms with large closets that could possibly turn this home into a 5 bedroom house!  Large kitchen with all appliances, a living room overlooking the amazing property and a split bedroom style home completes the main level.  The main floor owner's suite has a large walk-in closet and private bath.  The lower level has a spacious family room, laundry room and utility area along with 2 more rooms with large closets.  Home Details:  New AC and furnace in August 2023.  Pellet stove included. New front porch.   The property also includes a 12X16 outbuilding and a 10X12 shed.
